definitions.definition: A type of comedo , manifesting as a small whitish bump of the skin due to retention of sebum and dead skin cells in a skin pore blocked by a thin layer of epithelium .
examples: Ruth knew that the whiteheads of her teenage acne were a temporary state of affairs, but that did nothing to quell her distress when an eruption hit just before prom.

definitions.definition: A species of passerine bird, endemic to New Zealand ( Mohoua albicilla ).
The blue-winged snow goose , Anser caerulescens caerulescens .
A domestic pigeon of a particular breed; a white-tailed monk.
